              <div>
                <strong>Want to minimize costs from the start?</strong>
                <p>An immigration attorney consultation ($150–$300, one-time) can tell you exactly which path is right for you before you pay any filing fees — potentially saving you thousands by choosing correctly.</p>
              </div>
